node.text:
“A collective is plural by nature, so it’s all about learning from new people but also bringing my own unique experience to the table.” Watch as Michelin-starred French chef @mory_sacko_  prepares his multi-cultural dish created to match Veuve Clicquot Rosé’s fresh floral notes and reveals the star ingredient in his signature sauce.
#NewMakersCollective #Aroundtheworld #MeetTheNewMaker #LiveClicquot
.
.
